  "name": "Morrison COU1 — CPB hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under cardiopulmonary bypass (CPB) conditions. Intended use: identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device at Model Risk Level 2. Full 13-factor assessment performed; 7 factors assessed (all meeting required levels), 6 factors not assessed (acceptable at MRL 2). Structured context-of-use link is absent from this package per Minimal profile declaration; use scope is implied by Claim and Requirement prose only.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/morrison/req/cpb-hemolysis-mrl2",
