    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors achieved required levels for MRL 2. Six factors were not assessed per ASME V&V 40 Table 3 allowances for MRL 2. The CFD hemolysis model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions for a Class II device submission. Prediction error of 8.2% NIH is within the 15% acceptance threshold.",
